  <section> 
   <div class="container"> 
    <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1"> 
     <h3 style="text-align: center">Frequently Asked Questions</h3> 
     <div class="row"> 
      <div class="col-sm-6"> 
       <h4>How can I customize my tagboard‘s appearance?</h4> 
       <p>For free and Pro accounts, tagboards can have custom cover and avatar images, and embedded tagboards can be set to adopt the background and aesthetics of the hosting page. Advanced customization options are available for <a href="https://about.tagboard.com/enterprise">Enterprise accounts</a>.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="col-sm-6"> 
       <h4>Do you offer discounts for non-profits?</h4> 
       <p>Yes, we do consider discounts for certain non-profit (and non-commercial) groups and organizations. <a href="https://about.tagboard.com/contact">Contact us directly</a> for more information.</p> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
     <div class="row"> 
      <div class="col-sm-6"> 
       <h4>Can my tagboard auto-load new posts?</h4> 
       <p>Yes! That‘s what Presentation Mode and Tagboard Live are for — available to Enterprise accounts.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="col-sm-6"> 
       <h4>Do you offer a trial period?</h4> 
       <p>We have a free account that includes a tagboard to try out. If you‘d like a demo of Enterprise features, <a href="https://about.tagboard.com/demo">contact our sales team</a>.</p> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
